'''Apache Cordova'''，舊稱'''PhoneGap'''是一款[[開放原始碼|開放原始碼]]的行動裝置開發框架，旨在讓開發者使用[[HTML|HTML]]、[[Javascript|Javascript]]、[[CSS|CSS]]等Web APIs開發跨平臺的行動裝置應用程式<ref>{{cite web | url=http://phonegap.com/ | title=Easily create apps using the web technologies you know and love: HTML, CSS, and JavaScript | publisher=phonegap | accessdate=2013-05-30 | archive-date=2013-05-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130523124308/http://phonegap.com/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。原本由Nitobi公司開發，現在由[[Adobe_Systems|Adobe Systems]]擁有<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.adobe.com/aboutadobe/pressroom/pressreleases/201110/AdobeAcquiresNitobi.html |title=Adobe Announces Agreement to Acquire Nitobi, Creator of PhoneGap |publisher=Adobe.com |date=2011-10-03 |accessdate=2012-04-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120413181632/http://www.adobe.com/aboutadobe/pressroom/pressreleases/201110/AdobeAcquiresNitobi.html |archivedate=2012-04-13 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.quora.com/Andre-Charland/PhoneGap/answers |title=Andre Charland's Answers on PhoneGap |publisher=Quora |date= |accessdate=2012-04-07}}</ref>。

==發展歷程==
最早的PhoneGap起步于2009年在舊金山召開的iPhoneDevCamp大會<ref name="#1">http://www.eweek.com/c/a/Application-Development/PhoneGap-Simplifies-iPhone-Android-BlackBerry-Development-788189/</ref>，Nitobi的工程师Brock Whitten、Rob Ellis和Andre Charland在[[iOS|iOS]]系統內架設起Web介面和[[Objective-C|Objective-C]]之間的橋樑，讓開發人員得以使用HTML5、JavaScript、CSS等web標準技術便捷開發原生程式，實現一次編譯到處執行。其“橋接Web與iPhone SDK之間縫隙”的理念得到歡迎<ref name="#1"/>。

2011年10月4日，Adobe正式宣布收購Nitobi軟件<ref>{{cite web |last=Shankland |first=Stephen |url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-30685_3-20114857-264/adobe-buys-phonegap-typekit-for-better-web-tools/ |title=Adobe buys PhoneGap, TypeKit for better Web tools | Deep Tech - CNET News |publisher=News.cnet.com |date=2011-10-03 |accessdate=2012-04-07 |archive-date=2012-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120729171734/http://news.cnet.com/8301-30685_3-20114857-264/adobe-buys-phonegap-typekit-for-better-web-tools/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。PhoneGap的代碼貢獻給了Apache軟件基金會，但保留了PhoneGap的商标所有权，並命名为Apache Callback。1.4版发布后，接著Apache Callback的名称变更为'''Apache Cordova'''。Cordova是街道的名字，在開發團隊附近。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.h-online.com/open/news/item/Apache-Cordova-gets-a-new-look-1440114.html |title=Apache Cordova gets a new look - The H Open Source: News and Features |publisher=H-online.com |date=2012-02-22 |accessdate=2012-04-07 |archive-date=2013-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131207055534/http://www.h-online.com/open/news/item/Apache-Cordova-gets-a-new-look-1440114.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>Adobe Dreamweaver 5.5版本为phonegap提供开发环境。

早期版本的PhoneGap需要使用蘋果電腦來開發iOS應用程序，而Windows Mobile應用程序則是使用Windows平台開發出來的。2012年9月之後，「 PhoneGap Build」服務推出，可以讓程序員將他的源代碼上傳到「雲編譯器」，產生應用程式每一個所支援平台的安裝包<ref>Klint Finley.
[http://techcrunch.com/2012/09/24/adobe-launches-hosted-phonegap-build-service-for-creating-cross-platform-mobile-apps/ "Adobe Launches Hosted PhoneGap Build Service For Creating Cross-Platform Mobile Apps"] {{Wayback|url=http://techcrunch.com/2012/09/24/adobe-launches-hosted-phonegap-build-service-for-creating-cross-platform-mobile-apps/ |date=20141220214427 }}.
2012.</ref>。

==設計理念==

PhoneGap是一個行動設備的[[API|API]]接口集，利用JavaScript存取這些接口可以調用諸如攝影機、羅盤等硬體系統資源。配合上一些基於[[HTML5|HTML5]]、[[CSS3|CSS3]]技術的[[UI|UI]]框架，如jQuery Mobile、Dojo Mobile或Sencha Touch，開發者得以快速地開發跨平台App而不需要編寫任何的原生代碼。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://cordova.apache.org/index.html#about | title=Apache Cordova is a platform for building native mobile applications using HTML, CSS and JavaScript | accessdate=2013-05-30 | archive-date=2013-06-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130606120854/http://cordova.apache.org/index.html#about | dead-url=no }}</ref>

注意到因為PhoneGap本身仍是一個原生程式，為App打包時依然需要用到這些系統平台的SDK。

PhoneGap Framework可以用多種行動應用程式平台開發，例如：ViziApps、<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.viziapps.com |title=Create Mobile and Web Apps with HTML5 and JavaScript |publisher=ViziApps.com |date= |accessdate=2012-04-07 |archive-date=2012-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120331122805/http://viziapps.com// |dead-url=yes }}</ref> Worklight、<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.worklight.com |title=Mobile Application Platform and Tools |publisher=Worklight |date=2012-01-16 |accessdate=2012-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120419142918/http://www.worklight.com/ |archive-date=2012-04-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.phonegap.com/2011/06/27/how-phonegap-plays-an-important-part-in-our-enterprise-offering/ |title=How PhoneGap plays an important part in our Enterprise offering « PhoneGap |publisher=Phonegap.com |date=2011-06-27 |accessdate=2012-04-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120415220543/http://phonegap.com/2011/06/27/how-phonegap-plays-an-important-part-in-our-enterprise-offering |archivedate=2012-04-15 }}</ref>Convertigo<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.convertigo.com |title=Open Source Mobile Enablement and Enterprise Mashups |publisher=Convertigo |date= |accessdate=2012-04-07 |archive-date=2012-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120412042140/http://www.convertigo.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://phonegap.com/2011/07/07/convertigo-mobilizer-uses-phonegap-build-apis/ |title=Convertigo Mobilizer Uses PhoneGap Build APIs « PhoneGap |publisher=Phonegap.com |date=2011-07-07 |accessdate=2012-04-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120513040808/http://phonegap.com/2011/07/07/convertigo-mobilizer-uses-phonegap-build-apis/ |archivedate=2012-05-13 }}</ref>、Tiggr和appMobi<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.appmobi.com |title=Create Mobile and Web Apps with HTML5 and JavaScript | |publisher=appMobi.com |date= |accessdate=2012-04-07 |archive-date=2012-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120413165752/http://www.appmobi.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> ，也可以选择PhoneGap Build编译工具。

由於使用Web技術，PhoneGap程式的載入和UI介面的反應都比原生的程式慢<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.sapandiwakar.in/technical/api-research-study-iphone-and-android-applications/ | title="Titanium vs Phonegap vs Native application development" | accessdate=2013-05-30 | author=Sapan Diwakar | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130624144410/http://www.sapandiwakar.in/technical/api-research-study-iphone-and-android-applications/ | archivedate=2013-06-24 }}</ref>。[[Adobe|Adobe]]警告開發者，由於使用PhoneGap框架開發的程式執行速度可能會太慢或使用體驗不夠“原生”，而被[[蘋果公司|蘋果]]應用商店拒絕上架<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.adobe.com/devnet/phonegap/articles/apple-application-rejections-and-phonegap-advice.html | title=PhoneGap advice on dealing with Apple application rejections | publisher=Adobe System | date=29 October 2012 | accessdate=2013-05-30 | author=Andrew Trice | archive-date=2013-05-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130518091415/http://www.adobe.com/devnet/phonegap/articles/apple-application-rejections-and-phonegap-advice.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.adobe.com/devnet/phonegap/articles/creating-apps-with-phonegap-lessons.html | title=Creating apps with PhoneGap: Lessons learned | publisher=Adobe System | date=17 September 2012 | accessdate=2013-05-30 | author=Greg Avola | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130518085321/http://www.adobe.com/devnet/phonegap/articles/creating-apps-with-phonegap-lessons.html | archive-date=2013-05-18 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

